Description: Neyn sends a team of vampire slayers to kill Staz and rescue her daughter. But does Fuyumi even want to be saved?
Title: BLOOD LAD, VOL. 4
Author: Yuuki Kodama

Description: Ichigo Kurosaki sees dead people and helps usher them safely into the afterlife. In this volume, Ichigo heads to the palace of the Soul King for training.
Title: BLEACH, VOL. 59
Author: Tite Kubo

Description: Is this the end of humanity? It sure looks that way when what is left of mankind must go into hiding to escape the giant humanoids known as the Titans.
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 1
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: The identity of the Titans who have been destroying the walls is revealed, but has their treachery been discovered too late to save humanity?
Title: ATTACK ON TITAN, VOL. 11
Author: Hajime Isayama

Description: From the publisher: “A group of sinners who bear the guilt of the seven deadly sins has been gathered in an old courthouse to face judgement. Who will the gavel fall on first?”
Title: JUDGE, VOL. 3
Author: Yoshiki Tonogai

Description: In this latest volume, Naruto stands up to Tobi and the Allied Shinobi Forces battle the Ten-Tailed Beast.
Title: NARUTO, VOL. 64
Author: Masashi Kishimoto

Description: Tomoko Kuroki comes to a harsh realization when she begins high school: she's horribly unpopular!
Title: NO MATTER HOW I LOOK AT IT, IT'S YOU GUYS' FAULT I'M NOT POPULAR!, VOL. 2
Author: Nico Tanigawa

Description: Tomoe reveals that he is dying from a 500-year-old curse. Will Nanami be able to save him?
Title: KAMISAMA KISS, VOL. 14
Author: Julietta Suzuki

Description: Summer is over and Ryuji and Taiga are back in school, but the most dramatic development happens at home, when Taiga’s father returns.
Title: TORADORA!, VOL. 6
Author: Yuyuko Takemiya and Zekkyo

Description: A teenager signs up to help mythical creatures assimilate into society. How will he contend being roommates with a sexy snake woman, an alluring centaur girl and a harpy who likes to flirt?
Title: MONSTER MUSUME, VOL. 1
Author: Okayado
